{"word":"G5093 - τίμιος - tímios - tim'-ee-os - Dear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τίμιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tímios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tim'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அருமையான, கனமுள்ள, விலையேறப்பெற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. precious"},{"paragraph":"2. held in honor.esteemed.dear"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Including the comparative <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>timio&#x0304;teros</b> and the superlative <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;&#x03C9;&#x0301;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>timio&#x0304;tatos</b>; from <a href=\"#/G5092 - τιμή - timḗ - tee-may'/5092\">G5092</a>; <i>valuable</i>, that is, (objectively) <i>costly</i>, or (subjectively) <i>honored</i>, <i>esteemed</i>, or (figuratively) <i>beloved:</i> - dear, honourable, (more, most) precious, had in reputation.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5091/5091\">G5091</a>, <a href=\"#/G5092/5092\">G5092</a>, <a href=\"#/G5093/5093\">G5093</a>, <a href=\"#/G5094/5094\">G5094</a>"}]}